vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 1 to exercise the first of two, one-year renewal options, to the service contract with Standard Insurance Company to provide voluntary insurance benefits to employees and eligible retirees, a self-funded vendor-administered Employee Benefits Program - No cost consideration to the City (to be funded by employee and retiree premiums through payroll deductions)
